<br>
That's a load of crap.  I had Improved Reclaim the moment I dinged 59, and haven't regretted it for a moment.  I personally recruit lower level magicians to pet groups in PoNightmare.<br>
<br>
Since with IR I can resummon pets mana free and even rebuff them, the only shortcoming I have come across is early root breaks.  That's where the second magician comes in.  All he/she has to do is send their pet in as soon as I reclaim my pet, then back it off when I send my new pet in.  Usually they chain with me until lom, then send their pet in between my pets for support until they have mana again. We both get experience, I get to solo a lot safer, and neither of us is lfg.<br>
  <br>
The best thing is that we can add others  to our little partnership over time until we have a full group.  I give preference to magicians, but almost anyone can help.<br>
<br>
If I can't find a magician partner, no biggie.  I can use ANY class to help as long as they have J or T Boots, or have Run Speed 3 or SoW, or can snare/root.  All they have to do is a minimal amount of damage (with range attacks or spells) to slightly outaggro me (I pull with Burst of Flame, then follow up with Malosini), my pets and I do all the major work, and my duo partner keeps the mob busy running in a tight circle  when/if pet root breaks.<br>
<br>
I usually ask someone in the zone already lfg if they can solo.  If they say they can't, or it's too risky, then I offer them the alternative to lfg.  They can get experience in a minimally supportive, but unavoidably essential role until we have enough to make a regular group, or they can continue to lfg.  They usually decide not to lfg and go for the easy experience.  If they are on the low side of the 50's spectrum, the experience for them is very very nice.  The experience for me is better than soloing in any Luclin zone, so I come out a winner too. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xymryk>Xymryk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 224<br> <font color=#333333>(12/26/02 6:47:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=330.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Leve 59?</span><hr size=1> ///PoP groups are good exp but hard to get in when 4 other mages over 60 are LFG too.////<br>
